settings.title: The Larken Difference
settings.content:
LUXURIOUSLY SOFT, EASY TO CARE FOR FABRICS

You don’t have time for high-maintenance clothes so we focus on designing versatile, machine-washable pieces. We carefully select breathable, ultra-soft fabrics that can endure the demands of motherhood and save time.

ALWAYS ELASTIC, HARDWARE AND TAG-FREE

Your skin and baby’s skin are incredibly sensitive. And when the baby is hungry or you’re multi-tasking, there’s no time to fumble with elastic, snaps, zippers or buttons. Our essentials are always elastic, hardware and tag-free for ease of use and superior comfort.

DESIGNED FOR ALL STAGES OF MOTHERHOOD

We thoughtfully design pieces that don’t look like the standard maternity or nursing garments and that adapt to your changing body and needs so you can love them whether you’re donning a bump or pump, nursing, or years into your journey through motherhood.

A NAME MEANING FIERCE

Motherhood is beautiful, but it isn’t always easy. Larken is a name that means fierce and was chosen out of a recognition that all of our journeys to and through motherhood are often a series of highs and lows, magical moments and messy struggles. We are inspired by our customers and committed to helping you feel your best at any stage of motherhood

Essential bras for nursing/pumping. So comfortable, a million times better than other bras with hooks and snaps. Hold the bottles for hands free pumping really well allowing me to get stuff done while I pump. I am so thankful I found these bras, I truly don't think I would be able to still be pumping without them. Initially bought one then 2 more now I have 5, one for each day of the work week. I wear it around the clock, so comfortable to sleep in, makes that middle of the night pump less annoying.

Eliza D.

I bought 2 bras and absolutely love them. I delivered my baby at 27 weeks last week and one of the only things I can do for him is pump. These bras have been an absolute life saver, I even sleep in them so in the middle of the night I can be hands free.

Kelsey A.

I love the Larken so so much. This is by far the best and most comfortable nursing bra I’ve ever used. I have a 7 week old and wear this every single day. It is so much more comfortable than any of the previous bras I’ve tried. It’s especially nice to be able to use this to pump rather than using an entirely different pumping bra. I have 4 kids and wish I’d had this for my other 3! Breastfeeding can be difficult so it’s amazing to have this to make nursing and pumping easier and a LOT more comfortable!

Caroline E.

The Larken Signature Tank is ridiculously comfortable. It has the right amount of tightness to support my belly and is long enough to keep me fully covered, unlike many of the other tanks I've tried.

Amanda, 9 Months Pregnant With Twins
